```python
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

# ÏùºÎ≥Ñ Îß§Ï∂ú Î°úÍ∑∏
df_sales = pd.DataFrame({
    "store": ["A"]*10 + ["B"]*10,
    "date": pd.to_datetime(
        ["2025-12-01","2025-12-02","2025-12-03","2025-12-04","2025-12-05",
         "2025-12-06","2025-12-07","2025-12-08","2025-12-09","2025-12-10"]*2
    ),
    "orders": [20,22,21,23,40,24,23,22,21,20,   18,19,20,18,17,16,15,14,13,12],
    "revenue":[2000,2200,2100,2300,5200,2400,2350,2250,2150,2050,
              1800,1900,2000,1850,1700,1600,1500,1400,1300,1200]
})

# Ï†ïÏ±Ö(Í∞ÄÍ≤©/ÌîÑÎ°úÎ™®) ‚Äî start_dateÎ∂ÄÌÑ∞ Ïú†Ìö®, Í∞ôÏùÄ storeÏóê Ïó¨Îü¨ Î≤à Î∞îÎÄî Ïàò ÏûàÏùå
df_policy = pd.DataFrame({
    "store": ["A","A","B","B"],
    "start_date": pd.to_datetime(["2025-12-01","2025-12-05","2025-12-01","2025-12-07"]),
    "policy_type": ["BASE","PROMO","BASE","PROMO"],
    "target_aov": [100, 120, 100, 110]   # AOV(=revenue/orders) Î™©Ìëú
})
display(df_sales, df_policy)
```

# ÌíÄÏù¥

```python
df_sales_sorted = df_sales.copy().sort_values(by=['date','store',])
df_policy_sorted = df_policy.copy().sort_values(by=['start_date','store',]).rename(columns={'start_date':'date'})
df_merged = pd.merge_asof(df_sales_sorted, df_policy_sorted, on='date', by='store')
display(df_merged)
df_merged['aov'] = df_merged['revenue']/df_merged['orders']
df_merged['gap_aov'] = df_merged['aov']-df_merged['target_aov']
df_merged['is_bad'] = df_merged['gap_aov']<=-15
display(df_merged)
df_merged['w_sum'] = df_merged['orders'] * df_merged['gap_aov']

store_feat = df_merged.groupby('store', as_index=False).agg(
    days=('date','count'),
    bad_days=('is_bad','sum'),
    gap_mean=('gap_aov','mean'),
    w_sum=('w_sum','sum'),
    orders_sum=('orders','sum')
)
store_feat['gap_wavg'] = store_feat['w_sum'] / store_feat['orders_sum']
store_feat = store_feat.drop(columns=['w_sum','orders_sum']).sort_values('gap_wavg')
display(store_feat)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
fig1, axes = plt.subplots(ncols=1, nrows=2, figsize=(7,6))
stores = ['A','B']
for idx, store in enumerate(stores):
    r = df_merged[df_merged['store']==store]
    r_scatter =df_merged[(df_merged['store']==store)&(df_merged['is_bad'])]
    axes[idx].plot(r['date'], r['aov'])
    axes[idx].plot(r['date'], r['target_aov'], color = 'gray', linestyle='--')
    axes[idx].scatter(r_scatter['date'], r_scatter['aov'], color='red')
    axes[idx].plot(r['date'], r['target_aov']-15, color = 'gray', linestyle='--')
    axes[idx].grid(False)
    axes[idx].set_title(f'{store} AOV vs Target')
    axes[idx].set_xlabel('date')
    axes[idx].set_ylabel('aov')
fig2, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(7,4))
ax.bar(store_feat['store'],store_feat['gap_wavg'])
ax.axhline(0, color='gray', linestyle='--')
ax.set_title("Weighted Avg AOV Gap (orders-weighted)")
ax.grid(False)
plt.show()
